ng a Turing-like instability\nand pattern formation. We find that for models in which particles diffuse off\nlattice, such as the Doi model, reactions lead to a spurious enhancement of the\neffective diffusion coefficients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Oct 2017 22:22:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Oct 2017 22:47:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Dec 2017 18:03:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
