result establishes that in general our improved upper bound is non\nachievable, but whether it is asymptotically achievable or not remains open.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Oct 2017 01:31:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-09"}
