 rates. In addition, geographic investigation of model residuals revealed\nclusters of counties where observed rates were much higher (and much lower)\nthan expected conditioned upon county variables.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Oct 2017 15:36:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-09"}
